<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#947721">{الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِينَ}</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">وينحصرُ في أربعةِ فصُولٍ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
